article_title: The Doctor Won't See You Now

article_metadata.author: Sally Pipes

og.description: As Obamacare exchange policies grow more expensive in the coming years, provider networks will only grow narrower. Patients may find themselves with coverage but without access to care -- unless they're willing to pay the doctor or hospital of their choice vast sums out of pocket.
